videos.description: Arizona's Kobi Simmons leaps up to try and finish a dunk off an alley-oop pass, but he is unable to complete the slam.
videos.headline: Simmons whiffs on an alley-oop dunk attempt

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen hits a three-pointer in the first against Washington State to remain perfect from beyond the arc in the game.
videos.headline: Markkanen hits third 3-pointer of first half

videos.description: Washington State's Ike Iroegbu gets up for the monster dunk off the toss from Malachi Flynn.
videos.headline: Washington State's Iroegbu slams down huge dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Chance Comanche makes the one-handed dunk off the great bounce pass from Allonzo Trier.
videos.headline: Trier's pass sets up Comanche for the one-handed dunk
